pageContext.claim: “Only a few people showed up for the so-called Impeachment rallies over the weekend. The numbers were anemic, no spirit, no hope. More importantly, No Collusion, No Obstruction!”
pageContext.analysis: The Mercury News reported more than 140 rallies planned throughout southern California calling for Trump’s impeachment. Reports said the rallies varied in size from a couple dozen to a couple hundred. Regardless, more than “a few” people showed up.
